OWNER GOALS & PATIENCE METER
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- Goals auto-generated at the start of each season (on generate-schedule):
  80+ avg OVR → Win championship + 12 wins
  75–79 OVR  → Make playoffs + 10 wins
  70–74 OVR  → 8 wins + develop a young star (age ≤25, 75+ OVR, 10+ games)
  Below 70   → 6 wins + develop a young star + stay under the salary cap
- Goals stored in owner_goals table (season, goal_type, target_value, achieved)
- Evaluation runs at season advance (evaluateOwnerGoals in OwnerGoalsService):
  Checks wins, playoffs appearance, championship, player development, cap
  compliance; marks each goal achieved = 1 or 0
- Owner patience (0–100, default 75) adjusts after evaluation:
  All goals met → +15 / Majority met → +5 / One met → -10 / None → -20
  Clamped to 0–100
- Patience drops trigger news events:
  Below 50: "Owner Growing Impatient"
  Below 25: "Owner Issues Final Warning"

